abstract: Protesters are gearing up for the weekend, a sociologist has released a study of visitors to occupywallst.org, and Alec Baldwin took some heat and responded to it.
snippet: Protesters are gearing up for the weekend, a sociologist has released a study of visitors to occupywallst.org, and Alec Baldwin took some heat and responded to it.
lead_paragraph: Protesters are gearing up as the weekend approaches - and taking in a little culture. An Occupy Wall Street-endorsed group, Occupy Museums, plans to occupy the Museum of Modern Art, the Frick and the New Museum beginning at 3 p.m. Thursday. [Paddy Johnson]
